            <p>
                Translations fee will differ due to the customers' evaluation.
                <br> A translator's evaluation will be decided by the average points of the points earned by each order.
                <br> A translator with high evaluation would be pay more.
                <br> Also, translators with high evaluation will be posted on the top list of translator search engine, thus making them easier to be appointed.
            </p>
            <div class="flex-container">
                <div class="box ">
                    <h3>  What is the ★ mark of translator evaluation?</h3>
                    <p>
                        Evaluate the translators from a 1~5 scale.
                        <br>
                        <br>Please evaluate the 4 categories below with a scale from 1~5.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li>1. How are the choices and unification of terms?</li>
                        <li>2. How does the writing style fit with the document?</li>
                        <li>3. Please evaluate the total quality.</li>
                        <li>4. How did the translator handle the order? (meeting the deadline, exchanging messages, etc.)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-container">
                <div class="box ">
                    <h3>  Concepts of evaluation method. </h3>
                    <p>
                        Total points earned by each order ÷ total orders ＝ average evaluation.
                        <br>
                    </p>
                    <span>
                        <p>EX)</p>
                    </span>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li>Order A 5 pt.</li>
                        <li>Order B 4 pt.</li>
                        <li>Order C 3 pt.</li>
                        <li>Order D 2 pt.</li>
                        <li>Order E 1 pt.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li>Average 3.4/5 pt ＝ Translator's evaluation. </li>
                        <li>★ marks will be posted. </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-container">
                <div class="box ">
                    <h3> To receive good translation evaluation </h3>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li> ・Confirm all cautions of the customer's request.</li>
                        <li> ・Understand the overall picture before starting the translation.</li>
                        <li> ・Always ask questions if you do not understand the content.</li>
                        <li> ・Always double check before you deliver (cautions/specific terms, etc.)</li>
                        <li> ・When necessary, leave comments on specific areas for further interaction.</li>
                        <li> ・Always deliver by the deadline (*Immediately notify the customer and office if you are going to be late.)</li>
                        <li> ・Follow up carefully and politely after delivery (answering customer questions and so)</li>
                    </ul>
